additionalInfo.description:
Straight passthrough of application data from Guidewire’s ai table to stage load. This table will be a truncate and load of incremental data.

We will want to join to advrxxchangedbeans on systemid and cmmcontainer in the source query to limit the data to incremental records. As  part of this, we’ll need to add $$m_strtdt and $$m_enddt to the mapping as parameters and add as a join condition against adddt and addtm as well.
